source/Giant_panda\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Footage released on July 29 shows the playful cub effortlessly balancing on a bar before defying gravity with a daring upside-down flip.\", \"from\": 462, \"to\": 598, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"With remarkable strength and agility, the cub clings to the bar, even managing to stand on a ring attached.\", \"from\": 599, \"to\": 706, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"These impressive feats are made possible by the research base's commitment to enriching panda's environment.\", \"from\": 708, \"to\": 816, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Wooden frames and rings are part of the facilities designed to stimulate natural behaviors and prevent boredom.\", \"from\": 817, \"to\": 928, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This holistic approach ensures the physical, mental well-being of the beloved creatures.\", \"from\": 929, \"to\": 1017, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Renowned worldwide for its panda conservation efforts, Chengdu Research Base is a vital sanctuary for giant pandas, red pandas and other endangered species.\", \"from\": 1019, \"to\": 1175, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1074, \"end\": 1081, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chengdu\", \"score\": 0.8008454466927326, \"rank\": 0.24868038402005344, \"text\": \"Chengdu\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chengdu\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chengdu\"}, {\"begin\": 1135, \"end\": 1145, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Red_panda\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"red pandas\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Red_panda\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Red_panda\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Through breeding, research and education, the base plays a crucial role in safeguarding these precious animals for future generations.\", \"from\": 1176, \"to\": 1310, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00